            >
              <div
                class="home-number-feature"
                style="background-color: #1f2937; color:white;"
              >
                <div class="text-h4" style="color: #30f1e1;">Simple to use</div>
                <div class="">
                  A telecoil lets you connect directly to hearing loops in
                  public venues and at home with no extra equipment needed.
                  Simply switch your hearing aid or implant to T-mode to tap
                  into clear, direct sound.
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="home-number-feature"
                style="background-color: #1f2937; color:white;"
              >
                <div class="text-h4" style="color: #30f1e1;">
                  Often Overlooked
                </div>
                <div class="">
                  Many hearing-aid and implant users are never informed that a
                  telecoil exists. Unaware of it, they miss out on any benefits
                  a Telecoil may provide.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

