            <div class="">
              Look for a physical switch, button, or app setting to toggle
              T-mode. Some devices switch automatically when near a loop.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="spacer-xs"></div>
          <div
            class="home-number-feature dotted"
            style="background-color: #15190d; color:white;"
          >
            <div class="text-h5" style="color: #30f1e1;">
              <span style="color:white;">3. </span>Test It Out
            </div>
            <div class="">
              Your telecoil will pick up sound in venues with hearing loops, or
              when using a neckloop provided by IR or FM systems. No extra
              equipment needed on your end.
            </div>
